# 🛡️ Cyber Threat Intelligence Dashboard

## Overview

A Cyber Threat Intelligence Dashboard developed using Python, Streamlit, Plotly, and the AbuseIPDB API to perform real-time IP reputation analysis and threat intelligence investigation.

The application enables security analysts to assess suspicious IP addresses by retrieving threat intelligence indicators such as Abuse Confidence Score, total abuse reports, ISP details, country information, domain information, and TOR exit node status.

---

## Features

* Real-time IP Reputation Analysis
* AbuseIPDB API Integration
* Threat Score Calculation
* Automated Risk Classification (Low, Medium, High)
* Country and ISP Identification
* TOR Exit Node Detection
* Interactive Security Dashboard
* Downloadable Threat Intelligence Reports

---

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Streamlit
* Plotly
* Requests
* REST API
* JSON
* AbuseIPDB API

